  "title": "Inductance",
  "concepts": [
    {
      "title": "Potential Drop Across Inductors",
      "conceptBody": "<h3><strong>Potential Drop Across Inductor&nbsp;</strong></h3><ul><li>When the current in the inductor is increasing</li></ul><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"207\" height=\"81\">&nbsp;</p><p>$\\left( {{V}_{\\text{a}}}&gt;{{V}_{\\text{b}}} \\right)$</p><p>$\\left( {{V}_{a}}-{{V}_{b}} \\right)=L\\left( \\frac{di}{dt} \\right)$</p><ul><li>When the current in the inductor is decreasing</li></ul><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"217\" height=\"79\"></p><p>$\\left( {{V}_{\\text{b}}}-{{V}_{\\text{a}}} \\right)=L\\left| \\frac{di}{dt} \\right|$</p>",
      "position": 0,
      "qcConcept": "66a0db41c03b9dcaf1afe0e1"
    },
    {
      "title": "Combination of Inductors",
      "conceptBody": "<h3><strong>Combination of Inductors</strong></h3><p><strong>1.Series combination&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"432\" height=\"104\">&nbsp;</strong></p><p>$V=\\left( {{V}_{1}}+{{V}_{2}} \\right)$</p><p>${{\\text{L}}_{eq}}\\left( \\frac{di}{dt} \\right)={{\\text{L}}_{1}}\\left( \\frac{\\text{di}}{\\text{dt}} \\right)+{{\\text{L}}_{2}}\\left( \\frac{\\text{di}}{\\text{dt}} \\right)$</p><p>${{L}_{eq}}={{\\text{L}}_{1}}+{{\\text{L}}_{2}}$</p><p><strong>2.Parallel combination&nbsp;</strong></p><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"159\" height=\"154\"></p><p>$i={{i}_{1}}+{{i}_{2}}$&nbsp;</p><p>$\\left( \\frac{di}{dt} \\right)=\\left( \\frac{d{{i}_{1}}}{dt} \\right)+\\left( \\frac{d{{i}_{2}}}{dt} \\right)$&nbsp;</p><p>$\\frac{V}{{{L}_{eq}}}=\\frac{V}{{{L}_{1}}}+\\frac{V}{{{L}_{2}}}$ &nbsp;\\(\\therefore \\frac{1}{\\mathrm{~L}_{\\text {eq }}}=\\frac{1}{\\mathrm{~L}_1}+\\frac{1}{\\mathrm{~L}_2}\\)</p>",
      "position": 1,
      "qcConcept": "66a0db41c03b9dcaf1afe0e2"
    },
    {
      "title": "Energy Stored in Inductors",
      "conceptBody": "<h3><strong>Energy Stored in Inductor&nbsp;</strong></h3><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"205\" height=\"148\">&nbsp;</p><p>In an LR circuit, using KVL</p><p>$\\in =\\,\\,L\\,\\,\\left( \\frac{di}{dt} \\right)\\,\\,+\\,\\,iR \\,\\,[Multiply\\,with\\,\\,(idt)]$</p><p>$\\int{\\,\\in \\,}\\,\\text{i}\\,\\text{d t}\\,=\\,\\,\\int{\\,L\\,i d\\,i}\\,\\,+\\,\\,\\int{{{\\text{i}}^{2}}}\\,Rdt$</p><p>$\\Delta \\,\\,{{W}_{\\text{b}}}=\\frac{1}{2}\\text{L}{{\\text{i}}^{2}}+Heat\\,dissipated\\,in\\,resistor$</p>",
      "position": 2,
      "qcConcept": "66a0db42c03b9dcaf1afe0e3"
    },
    {
      "title": "Magnetic Energy Density",
      "conceptBody": "<h3>Magnetic Energy Density</h3><p>$Energy\\,density\\,\\,\\,=\\,\\,\\, \\left( \\frac{u}{Al} \\right)=\\frac{1}{2}\\frac{L{{i}^{2}}}{(Al)}$</p><p>$=\\,\\,\\frac{1}{2}\\,\\,\\frac{\\left( {{\\mu }_{0}}\\,\\pi \\,r_{1}^{2}\\,\\,{{n}^{2}}\\,\\,l \\right){{i}^{2}}}{\\pi \\,r_{1}^{2} l}$</p><p>$=\\,\\,\\frac{1}{2}\\,\\,\\left( {{\\mu }_{0}}\\,\\,{{n}^{2}} \\right){{i}^{2}}$</p><p>$=\\,\\,\\,\\frac{1}{2{{\\mu }_{0}}}\\,\\,\\,{{\\left( {{\\mu }_{0}}\\,ni \\right)}^{2}}\\,\\,=\\left( \\frac{1~{{B}^{2}}}{2\\,{{\\mu }_{0}}} \\right)$</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "position": 3,
      "qcConcept": "66a0db42c03b9dcaf1afe0e4"
    }
  ],
